plyTime":"2019-04-06T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"我係個老公真係即離婚 <br />\n屌你老母美好家庭就係呢啲賭撚搞衰哂<br />\n仲要為人師表 死咗去啦"},{"pid":"cd315ea5bad383a58fa78bc7b36550bf9baccba0","tid":1094140,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:42:28.000Z","msg":"呃七十萬先有一個家長報警 <br />\n<br />\n到底平時冇人舉報的話 呢啲名校袋咗幾多？"},{"pid":"e1a26f4caa58f34dd118987bb17fd89de8a9de44","tid":1094140,"uid":15646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e93d7ed62f6d53c75940b76f1163fa37b82f2a7","tid":1094140,"uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7a207c10b46c5516886e84dc58f4f22bf49974f1","tid":1094140,"uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:14:51.000Z","msg":"成班屋企人儍<br />\n<br />\n本來人上人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:31:59.000Z","msg":"本來有錢有事業有家庭，最後有咁既下場真係完全唔抵可憐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"仲要講到岀撚左黎改過自身就真係冇事咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢d仆街死不足惜啦屌"},{"pid":"3e739405171152348a9584b7d37fb3ac6b284b45","tid":1094140,"uid":191701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"今晚大灣區反貪局2019"},{"pid":"0e2229d2c9ae240f4dd4389e54c620ff288ee107","tid":1094140,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:06:49.000Z","msg":"根本賭仔仲衰過殺人放火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53feedfb3e45228a65577e7f95f41fa64a649ef","tid":1094140,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1a26f4caa58f34dd118987bb17fd89de8a9de44","tid":1094140,"uid":15646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e93d7ed62f6d53c75940b76f1163fa37b82f2a7","tid":1094140,"uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7a207c10b46c5516886e84dc58f4f22bf49974f1","tid":1094140,"uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T08:14:51.000Z","msg":"成班屋企人